Text: Confirmation of meetingThanks for introducing me as a speaker at the Power conference As per our conversation please find enclosed my resume I will come to your office at PM Friday May Please let me know if the dress code is casual or formal Thanks again for taking the time to talk to me regarding opportunities at Enron ResumeSanjeevKhannadoc Sanjeev K Khanna MSc PEng Director Quantitative Risk Management PGE Energy Trading Louisina Street Houston TX Email Tel Pager Cell PGE Energy Trading and any other company referenced herein which uses the PGE name or logo are not the same company as Pacific Gas and Electric Company the California utility These companies are not regulated by the California Public Utilities Commission and customers do not have to buy products from these companies in order to continue to receive quality regulated services from the utility ResumeSanjeevKhannadoc
